{"tid":1213403,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(五毛洗版) 叫你克制冷靜，武力降級嘅人，同政府口徑一致","createTime":"2019-06-13T01:33:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T12:40:26.000Z","uid":190928,"like":30,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"aeca5bb28077af5d6b9964818d8d8b6b3cfa4d03","tid":1213403,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:33:05.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">論係TG定連登，尋晚開始一大堆acc突然湧出嚟，叫人散，叫人降級，好多巴打信咗佢哋中晒伏。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">請唔俾佢哋迷惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n佢哋嘅目的就係要係後線 (連登，各大TG group) 亂人心，令你軟弱，減輕前線(警察防線)嘅工作壓力，最後令你哋被瓦解。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">佢哋最常用嘅手段，係恐嚇</span>，例如：<br />\n1. 收到風，X點準備用實彈，走呀！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. X點鐘清場，會出實彈，返屋企啦求吓你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 班狗打到癲咗，走啦！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n4. 唔好掟乜掟物，一陣間人哋有藉口升級武力，要醒少少，和平示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n5. 暴動罪坐好多年架，唔好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n請記住以上說話全部同政府，警察利益一致。就係想你弱，想你怯，想你散。你手段越弱，警察就越唔洗用啲係鏡頭前睇落核突嘅手段招呼你，減輕輿論壓力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">你越弱，佢越輕鬆</span>。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n面對呢啲言論，可以試吓咁諗：<br />\n和理非？2014年雨傘佔足三個月，大前日百萬行，結果呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好升級？尋日無升級，咪一樣開槍打頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再搞入暴動？而家777已經定性咗係暴動啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n請廣傳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"c650910034121c7ec9fd68dfe4801fb46cb32c94","tid":1213403,"uid":173849,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:35:04.000Z","msg":"五毛又開始分化00後同醜化泛民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36477235a2b69a6e53e6feb8f44ef56768015649","tid":1213403,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"37b4cdf67aecd1f3a124d004fd99e620650c7099","tid":1213403,"uid":41988,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:43:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3722371\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fen%2Fnews%2F3722371&d=OjLoGj31iMtRFsPqVtgEmoeonPPUtn1HApnj2AcFxYA%3D&h=9b9be4de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3722371</a><br />\n共產黨準備入港"},{"pid":"197968a5585c876572ceedb08fb280a8424fc44a","tid":1213403,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:46:54.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"97ed85462775c5e6e522ab52ce4435744a8aeba0","tid":1213403,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:54:59.000Z","msg":"唔好再幻想可以和理非就贏啦，求吓你哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"520b3f76b2281a24847fcd1a1515b18741424fce","tid":1213403,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:12:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3c727b5eef8d97d198674af4c3fe1801f00c7d8","tid":1213403,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T02:14:43.000Z","msg":"仲有話淨係用雞蛋做武器就夠<br />\n方太煮餸呀???"},{"pid":"23336c2a2615d54cf751e652c3f26d373d6464d5","tid":1213403,"uid":190928,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"c3c727b5eef8d97d198674af4c3fe1801f00c7d8","tid":1213403,"uid":59898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"